description:
BIGTREETECH Previews Upgraded SBC and Computer Module Featuring Rockchip RK3566
This month, BIGTREETECH expanded its single-board computer series with the debut of the BIGTREETECH Pi 2 and the BIGTREETECH CB2 computer module, both leveraging the Rockchip RK3566 SoC. These latest offerings showcase enhancements in Ethernet connectivity, memory, and storage, marking a notable evolution from their predecessors.
title: BIGTREETECH Previews Upgraded SBC and Computer Module Featuring Rockchip RK3566

Low-Cost Pocket Router with 2x 1GbE + 2x 2.5GbE ports
The LinkStar-H68K-1432 V2, Seeedstudio’s latest router, enhances network performance with updated hardware and design. It builds upon the predecessor LinkStar-H68K compact router, featuring advanced core components and connectivity options.
title: Low-Cost Pocket Router with 2x 1GbE + 2x 2.5GbE ports
